  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603230/extras/e59d25f87a283b0a69b1d037ee7e9d6f.poster.avif?t=1724770905\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603230/extras/e59d25f87a283b0a69b1d037ee7e9d6f.webm?t=1724770905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603230/extras/e59d25f87a283b0a69b1d037ee7e9d6f.mp4?t=1724770905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>■ Roguelike : Little Scavenger has a diverse and replayable world and permanent death as a reason to stay cautious.<br><br>■ Isometric top-down combat : The game takes inspiration from games like Diablo, Hades, and Dead Cells in the design of its combat.<br><br>■ Weapons and loot : Play with an abundance of weapons and tools that affects your playstyle in every run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603230/extras/ca28280f59ee89749736ec2e10cb2134.poster.avif?t=1724770905\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603230/extras/ca28280f59ee89749736ec2e10cb2134.webm?t=1724770905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603230/extras/ca28280f59ee89749736ec2e10cb2134.mp4?t=1724770905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603230/extras/6edf45cd009c7393dddbaa49900d12d1.poster.avif?t=1724770905\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603230/extras/6edf45cd009c7393dddbaa49900d12d1.webm?t=1724770905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603230/extras/6edf45cd009c7393dddbaa49900d12d1.mp4?t=1724770905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
